flowchart LR
    GEN[Gemini genera frames] --> V2[v2/ frames crudos]
    V2 --> REMBG[rembg U2Net<br/>remove_bg.py]
    REMBG --> NOBG[v2_nobg/ sin fondo]
    NOBG --> CROP[OpenCV Otsu + morph<br/>crop_to_bbox.py]
    CROP --> CUT[v2_nobg_cut/ recortados]
    CUT --> ASE[pixel-mcp + Aseprite<br/>rebuild_all.lua]
    ASE --> PNG[public/sprites/*.png<br/>Spritesheets horizontales]
    ASE --> JSON[public/sprites/*.json<br/>Metadata frames]
    ASE --> ASEFILE[assets/aseprite/*.aseprite<br/>Fuentes editables]

    JSON --> COMP[VotiSprite.tsx]
    PNG --> COMP
    COMP --> RENDER[Browser: canvas drawImage<br/>+ frame cycling por duration]

    style GEN fill:#8b5cf6,color:#fff
    style REMBG fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style CROP fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style ASE fill:#f59e0b,color:#000
    style COMP fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
